fields.name: Fixed Bracket Suspended Shelves
fields.description: High-quality light wood shelving. 8"x2" can hold up to 50 lbs. Used for storage in kitchen, bathroom, closet, bedroom, office or anywhere.

fields.name: Full-Body Vinyl Mannequin
fields.description: Full-Body, female mannequin for clothing and apparel. 5'7 size 0. Mannequins have head and hands, blank faces. Ivory vinyl material, can withstand heavy-duty coats etc.

fields.name: Pallet of Clay Bricks
fields.description: Clay Bricks with vertical holes used for construction. Eco-efficient hollow verticle holes. Made with raw clay, strong durability. Comes in a pallet of 500 bricks.

fields.name: Small Rolling File Cabinet
fields.description: Small 3-drawer aluminum file cabinet. Two 4" drawers and one 7" drawer. Sturdy aluminum holds up to 300lbs per drawer. Rolls on 4 small detachable wheels. Comes in light silver or dark charcoal.
